        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Uighur Intervention and Global Humanitarian Unified Response Act of 2018 or the UIGHUR Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill restricts executive agencies from procuring goods and services from foreign persons involved in China's mass detention of the Uyghurs, a predominantly Muslim Turkic ethnic group in Xinjiang province. It also places export controls on various technologies used to facilitate the mass detentions.<br> </p>]]></text>
